{"tid":1346433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（名不正則言不順）元朗發生嘅係恐怖襲擊！","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:47.000Z","uid":276044,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"568e28640ce819882ec6729c293529ef5597ee8a","tid":1346433,"uid":276044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcj6XpA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffcj6XpA.png&h=52e80ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家已經唔係鄉黑出嚟打人咁簡單，警黑勾結，放任佢哋無差別攻擊，完全係恐怖主義。<br />\n無論係向國際求助，定係自己出師，都應該搞講清楚對面係咩人！"},{"pid":"7bc51757c78e7eb69d56f0ecbfc43b5a24debfeb","tid":1346433,"uid":241363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdXXjDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdXXjDS.png&h=bda9fc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pg5h36k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpg5h36k.png&h=843fd962&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f60baf378a451647ca3dc398a0f8514f58046e09","tid":1346433,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96ddffa890c442354baf89fbe0d9cad032d6ae90","tid":1346433,"uid":236709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好只用恐怖襲擊(terrorism)<br />\n<br />\n要用國家恐怖主義(state terrorism)</span></span><br />\n<code>「國家恐怖主義」並沒有一個學術上或在國際上得到公認的官方定義。許多學者認為，由政府官方執行的行動可以被稱作「國家恐怖主義」。</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=8d5c7937\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n用terrorism係可以令班牛屎佬變恐怖分子<br />\n但同樣亦可以apply到我地到<br />\n<code>一般如果無clarify 既terrorism 通常係指一個地方入面有少數既人唔滿意制度，作出無差別攻擊。</code><br />\n<br />\n如果定義香港有terrorism，中共即刻可以衝入黎維穩。依家所有你見到有關surveillance and control measurements都係用terrorism 為名，作為監視及控制群眾手段。最初維吾爾族就係被定性為恐怖分子，到依家被送入再教育營。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔只中國，好多其他國家例如法國都係用terrorism 黎做維穩，標籤特定人群方便控制，如果唔搞清楚呢點好易送頭比人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用state terrorism，可以指控班牛屎佬同政府有路搞terrisom <br />\n劍指港共中共</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a4638efd1d419a573524858d122a73263f2ac0f","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"5442421f6cbf1d6f6e71317f79977309c99edf82","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29e4cb1b98f890e7db304105a1c90d5d8f1ce5","tid":1346433,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6d4d7478f2d551d96ef5f89f1863aefa0209b16","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f5785cf32da4e76a8c9484d7f6ddb94c8027c9","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7cebf9dc99f3dfa16a2b74ddfdb4584da5b7bc","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c60cc248ad7d02aa80d043fdf693197633563dc","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae2db75d4f87197c21e64e98507217187db4a3d","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139f85b0edb8843317fbfcdc52151672a9fe269","tid":1346433,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d5e0ecb219cdff925b543301a00c59fe8207985","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f18a54ea8bc8dda738a8a7e9a442d1b9f954c0b","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bdd525b4d32d1f188695fa722b871670f98570","tid":1346433,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d72ada20378befc326bf4f4c44ff6d6f545514","tid":1346433,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"[全民罷工] 一句講曬 罷定唔罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ec927dd6ffd6b0bd6067d0de7f17b2213d1ceb4","tid":1346433,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"}]}